sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as 👤 User
    participant B as Browser
    participant CRM as CRM SPA
    participant SSO as SSO Reborn
    participant API as Main API
    participant DB as Database

    U->>B: Mở hub.reborn.vn/crm/
    B->>CRM: Load index.html + JS
    CRM->>CRM: Check token cookie
    Note over CRM: Không có token
    CRM->>SSO: Redirect /oauth/authorize<br/>?client_id=crm&redirect_uri=...
    SSO-->>U: Hiển thị form login
    U->>SSO: Nhập email + password
    SSO->>SSO: Verify credentials
    SSO->>U: Redirect crm/login?code=xxx&state=yyy
    U->>CRM: Browser load /crm/login?code=...
    CRM->>SSO: POST /oauth/token với code
    SSO-->>CRM: { access_token, refresh_token, expires_in }
    CRM->>CRM: Lưu vào cookie token
    CRM->>SSO: GET /oauth/userinfo (Bearer)
    SSO-->>CRM: { id, name, email, roles, ... }
    CRM->>API: GET /api/permissions/me (Bearer)
    API->>DB: Lookup permissions
    DB-->>API: [CUSTOMER, INVOICE, ...]
    API-->>CRM: permissions array
    CRM->>CRM: setUserContext()
    CRM->>U: Render Dashboard
